<p>One of his messages, blew me away.&nbsp; &ldquo;What is IT? That other people have that other people seemingly don&rsquo;t.&rdquo;&nbsp; I had to pause to think about this myself.&nbsp; I am not sure I even know the answer. I hope I will in time. Until that day, I will keep my head down, avoiding the grenades and fighting as hard as I can. &nbsp;</p>
